  "spans": [
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0002",
      "text": " 182",
      "bbox": [
        518.28,
        723.59,
        537.71,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0003",
      "text": "The Service Parameters included in a page may be either requirements or capabilities.  Capabilities",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        539.97,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0004",
      "text": "indicate those FC-4 properties that describe the role and state of the node in the FC-4 (e.g., channel",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        69.65,
        540.08,
        80.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0005",
      "text": "or device for FC-SB-3, initiator or target for FCP-2, and similar values). Requirements indicate those",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        81.65,
        539.92,
        92.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0006",
      "text": "FC-4 properties that shall be agreed upon by both nodes for operation with a FC-4.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        93.65,
        462.1,
        104.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0007",
      "text": "7.1.4",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        118.97,
        118.24,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0008",
      "text": "Protocol",
      "bbox": [
        128.24,
        118.97,
        168.73,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0009",
      "text": "7.1.4.1  PA required by originator and responder",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        142.96,
        324.84,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0010",
      "text": "For each PRLI request page the Originator and Responder PA validity bits are set to one and valid",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        166.96,
        539.89,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0011",
      "text": "Originator and Responder PAs are specified.  Service Parameter requirements are set to those that",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        178.96,
        540.02,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0012",
      "text": "correspond to the combined understanding expected to be agreed to by the Responder, given the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.96,
        539.83,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0013",
      "text": "knowledge that the Originator PA has of the Responder PA.  Service Parameter capabilities are",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        202.96,
        539.98,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0014",
      "text": "those of the Originator only.  The specification of Service Parameters as either requirements or capa-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.96,
        539.92,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0015",
      "text": "bilities is specified in the corresponding FC-4 standard.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        226.96,
        338.59,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0016",
      "text": "For each LS_ACC response page, the Originator and Responder PA validity bits are set to one and",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        250.96,
        539.93,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0017",
      "text": "valid Originator and Responder PAs are specified.  Service Parameter requirements are set to those",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        262.96,
        539.96,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0018",
      "text": "that are agreed to by the Responder.  Service Parameter capabilities are those of the Responder",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        274.96,
        540.05,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0019",
      "text": "only.  Error responses are possible.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        286.96,
        253.19,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0020",
      "text": "Each page identifies a Binding mode PRLI operation between one image at the Originator Nx_Port",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        310.96,
        540.02,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0021",
      "text": "and one image at the Responder Nx_Port.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        322.96,
        283.22,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0022",
      "text": "7.1.4.2  PA required by originator, supported by responder",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        346.96,
        373.17,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0023",
      "text": "For each PRLI request page the Originator PA validity bit is set to one and the Responder PA validity",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        370.96,
        540.12,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0024",
      "text": "bit is set to zero.  A valid Originator PA is specified.  Service Parameter requirements are set to those",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        382.96,
        539.9,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0025",
      "text": "that correspond to the combined understanding expected to be agreed to by the Responder, given",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        394.96,
        540.0,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0026",
      "text": "the knowledge that the Originator PA has of the Responder PA.  Service Parameter capabilities are",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        406.96,
        539.96,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0027",
      "text": "those of the Originator only.  The specification of Service Parameters as either requirements or capa-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        418.96,
        539.92,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0028",
      "text": "bilities is specified in the corresponding FC-4 standard.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        430.96,
        338.59,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0029",
      "text": "For each LS_ACC response page the Originator PA validity bit is set to one and the Responder PA",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.96,
        539.96,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0030",
      "text": "validity bit is set to zero.  The Originator PA is returned.  Service Parameter requirements are set to",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        466.96,
        539.93,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0031",
      "text": "those that are agreed to by the Responder.  Service Parameter capabilities are those of the Re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        478.96,
        540.19,
        490.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0032",
      "text": "sponder only.  Error responses are possible.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        490.96,
        292.11,
        502.07
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0033",
      "text": "Each page identifies a Binding mode PRLI operation between one image at the Originator Nx_Port",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        514.96,
        540.02,
        526.07
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0034",
      "text": "and the Responder Nx_Port.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        526.96,
        222.72,
        538.07
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0035",
      "text": "7.1.4.3  PA supported by originator, required by responder",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        550.96,
        373.16,
        562.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0036",
      "text": "For each PRLI request page, the Originator PA validity bit is set to zero and the Responder PA valid-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        574.96,
        539.97,
        586.07
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0037",
      "text": "ity bit is set to one.  A valid Responder PA is specified.  Service Parameter requirements are set to",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        586.96,
        539.8,
        598.07
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0038",
      "text": "those that correspond to the combined understanding expected to be agreed to by the Responder,",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        598.96,
        540.15,
        610.07
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0039",
      "text": "given the knowledge that the Originator PA has of the Responder PA.  Service Parameter capabilities",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        610.96,
        539.92,
        622.07
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0040",
      "text": "are those of the Originator only.  The specification of Service Parameters as either requirements or",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        622.96,
        539.98,
        634.07
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0041",
      "text": "capabilities is specified in the corresponding FC-4 standard.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        634.96,
        360.33,
        646.07
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0042",
      "text": "For each LS_ACC response page, the Originator PA validity bit is set to zero and the Responder PA",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        659.02,
        539.99,
        670.13
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0043",
      "text": "validity bit is set to one.  The Responder PA is returned.  Service Parameter requirements are set to",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        671.02,
        539.9,
        682.13
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0044",
      "text": "those that are agreed to by the Responder.  Service Parameter capabilities are those of the Re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        683.02,
        540.19,
        694.13
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p201_s0045",
      "text": "sponder only.  Error responses are possible.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        695.02,
        292.1,
        706.13
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    }
  ],
